---
---

<section id="about">
    <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-number">01</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
        <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-text">
            <p>I'm a software engineer who moves between two worlds: building <strong>production iOS apps</strong> used by millions and crafting <strong>games and interactive experiences</strong> with small, scrappy teams.</p>
            <p>Most recently I was the <strong>sole iOS engineer at Adapter</strong>, an AI assistant startup, where I took the app from zero to the App Store in under a year. Before that, I spent years at <strong>Warby Parker</strong> building AR and measurement tools that Apple featured.</p>
            <p>I hold a Master's from <strong>Carnegie Mellon's Entertainment Technology Center</strong>, where I learned to think at the intersection of technology, storytelling, and design. That perspective shapes everything I build.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-tracks">
            <div class="track-card">
                <div class="track-icon">&gt;_</div>
                <div class="track-name">iOS Engineering</div>
                <div class="track-desc">Swift, SwiftUI, UIKit, ARKit, RealityKit. Hybrid native+WebView architectures. AI-native workflows.</div>
                <span class="track-tag">Primary Class</span>
            </div>
            <div class="track-card">
                <div class="track-icon">&#9670;</div>
                <div class="track-name">Game Development</div>
                <div class="track-desc">Godot, GDScript, C#. Global Game Jam veteran. Rapid prototyping with small teams under pressure.</div>
                <span class="track-tag track-tag-warm">Active Subclass</span>
            </div>
            <div class="track-card">
                <div class="track-icon">&#10047;</div>
                <div class="track-name">Creative &amp; Experimental</div>
                <div class="track-desc">AR prototypes, interactive installations, cross-disciplinary side projects. Tinkering is a core trait.</div>
                <span class="track-tag track-tag-gold">Passive Skill</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .about-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
    }

    .about-text {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .about-text p + p {
        margin-top: 1.25rem;
    }

    .about-text strong {
        color: var(--text);
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .about-tracks {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .track-card {
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .track-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--border-hover);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .track-icon {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    .track-card:nth-child(2) .track-icon {
        color: var(--accent-warm);
    }

    .track-card:nth-child(3) .track-icon {
        color: var(--accent-gold);
    }

    .track-name {
        font-family: var(--display);
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .track-desc {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--text-dim);
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .track-tag {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.6rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        background: var(--accent-glow);
        padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
        border-radius: 3px;
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .track-tag-warm {
        background: rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent-warm);
    }

    .track-tag-gold {
        background: rgba(255, 217, 61, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent-gold);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .about-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>